    %% Internal flows
    RESTServer -->|routes to| DataPlane
    GRPCServer -->|routes to| DataPlane
    KafkaServer -->|routes to| DataPlane
    DataPlane -->|dispatches to| ModelRegistry
    ModelRegistry -->|manages| InferencePool
    InferencePool -->|loads| SKLearn
    InferencePool -->|loads| XGBoost
    InferencePool -->|loads| LightGBM
    DataPlane -->|checks| Cache
    RESTServer -->|exports| Prometheus
    GRPCServer -->|exports| Prometheus
    Prometheus -->|served by| MetricsServer
    RESTServer -->|traces| OTel
    GRPCServer -->|traces| OTel

    %% External integrations
    KServeGW["KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP TLS"]
    KServeCtrl["KServe Controller"]
    PrometheusExt["Prometheus<br/>Scraper"]
    OTLPCollector["OTLP Collector"]
    KafkaBroker["Kafka Broker<br/>9092/TCP"]
    ModelStorage["Model Storage<br/>S3 / PVC"]

    KServeGW -->|"HTTP 8080/TCP"| RESTServer
    KServeGW -->|"gRPC 8081/TCP"| GRPCServer
    KServeCtrl -->|deploys| MLServer
    PrometheusExt -->|"scrapes 8082/TCP"| MetricsServer
    OTel -->|"exports traces"| OTLPCollector
    KafkaBroker <-->|"9092/TCP"| KafkaServer
    ModelStorage -->|"model artifacts"| ModelRegistry

